Returns `true` if the poll is a [`Poll::Ready`] value.

# Examples

```
# use core::task::Poll;
let x: Poll<u32> = Poll::Ready(2);
assert_eq!(x.is_ready(), true);

let x: Poll<u32> = Poll::Pending;
assert_eq!(x.is_ready(), false);
```
